  <summary date="2020-03-05T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Telework Metrics and Cost Savings Act

This bill requires a federal agency's telework policy to include information on (1) annual goals for increasing the telework participation rate, and (2) methods for collecting data related to cost savings achieved through telework.</summary>
